{"tid":2506660,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"用分鏡說話的漫畫《葬送的芙莉蓮》","createTime":"2021-04-27T12:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:50:49.000Z","uid":20673,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a39c73454430b675c6ded3e57c5c7680ce23ac2","tid":2506660,"uid":20673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.plurk.com/7jSR70aKBc0X0c7Z7PYafW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2F7jSR70aKBc0X0c7Z7PYafW.png&h=74e45066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見呢到仲未有好多人討論<br />\n可能係香港仲未係好多人認識所以好想推介下俾大家<br />\n絕對係一套一睇就會吸引你認唔住睇落去既漫畫<br />\n係漫畫入面大部分對白都係用黎搞笑,分鏡畫面先係呢套漫畫既精髓<br />\n而且經常睇睇下你就會明番之前既伏筆細節位<br />\n早期唔算好多戰鬥場面,但係一d都唔悶<br />\n有深度既周刊唔太多見,係近年少見出色既漫畫<br />\n會令人想買埋單行本既作品<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事概要<br />\n這是勇者們打倒魔王之後的故事。<br />\n<br />\n結束長達十年的冒險旅程，作為英雄凱旋歸來的人類族的勇者辛美爾、矮人族的戰士艾澤、人類族的僧侶海塔、精靈族的魔法使芙莉蓮接受國王表揚。剛好遇上50年一遇的流星雨，四人組相約50年後再度相聚觀看難得一見的流星雨。但在芙莉蓮和昔日的冒險夥伴依約再會欣賞流星雨的當夜，夥伴的逝世讓長壽的芙莉蓮感受到生死無常，也讓芙莉蓮開始深入探討生命的意義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.hotime.asia/p8/images01/20201209/d95e1fe1166242e0a72109d60e739193.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.hotime.asia%2Fp8%2Fimages01%2F20201209%2Fd95e1fe1166242e0a72109d60e739193.png&h=69e59bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20210316182622-cde725474e38f9722b04595facb9d0d4-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20210316182622-cde725474e38f9722b04595facb9d0d4-mobile.jpg&h=329f352c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2c4918f561bcfcb9a551cd3ad5c50e6cc9c3cc0","tid":2506660,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"好睇，辛美爾好撚靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e279d273e019aaa1485e6ba5ff660be55ec067c7","tid":2506660,"uid":20673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U5J2iJzHkUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU5J2iJzHkUM&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=00d92d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U5J2iJzHkUM</a>"},{"pid":"d0ed794e7e9d52990fc1e857b88c06ae7bb2da78","tid":2506660,"uid":10883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"有乜伏筆？"},{"pid":"dc9acace323ad701d969bc46c4f7381009605016","tid":2506660,"uid":20673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0ed794e7e9d52990fc1e857b88c06ae7bb2da78","tid":2506660,"uid":10883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"有乜伏筆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"好多細節位都係之後先知<br />\n<br />\nE.G. <br />\n勇士原來係中意芙莉蓮<br />\n<br />\n好多細節真係要留心睇同埋記得之前既畫面先會諗到<br />\n係咁好快咁睇既話只係會錯過左呢D細節"},{"pid":"6cee53238bef20e6f1c015f7df84d2b7e60cbb53","tid":2506660,"uid":63877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"之前已經大把人推呢套野啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲算少人討論咩"},{"pid":"121cfc79838bac62c803616547e3b6486793d089","tid":2506660,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"隔離po三百幾個正皮啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4498662411eb4b4cac20a5d954047863b9053b","tid":2506660,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121cfc79838bac62c803616547e3b6486793d089","tid":2506660,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"隔離po三百幾個正皮啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中post:<br />\n在異世界泛濫的時代，真正符合勇者之名的勇者，漫畫《葬送的芙莉蓮》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2113